{"type": "article", "id": 49143, "title": "蒂芙尼将开微信限时零售店，李宇春代言鬼塚虎 | 乙方日报", "description": "这里有营销和营销人相关的一切", "date": "2018-01-12T05:18:53Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 47011, "name": "《歌手》"}, {"id": 5773, "name": "CES"}], "category": 18, "column": 31, "author": 26306, "comment_count": 16, "praise_count": 39, "image": "img/article/article_show/201801121316253fu4r0QTKX7paI1E.png", "contents": "<h3 finallycleanhtml=\"true\" nocleanhtml=\"true\">明星又代言了啥</h3><p class=\"\"><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzA4MDYzNTAzMQ==&amp;mid=2652382463&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=b76d1b1a604e4320e7658235aa352d2b&amp;chksm=844db107b33a38116180cb328bad1c4570081a176b0dc8ccdec958fb43fd0b4f0e656a434185&amp;mpshare=1&amp;scene=1&amp;srcid=0111bDq6UsbUlTWenCZsQzTU&amp;key=d54b4a39ce7d6c1bf343907973590da842353d353a3ebc839814cf951e6039c86e1d17fe6bdc9974adae2145761e8dd5687f1d6224882d8e677da9605c6daa15cb8648da8ac1d32bed0abd7b6c1fe0e3&amp;ascene=0&amp;uin=MTIyNTYzODY0MA%3D%3D&amp;devicetype=iMac+MacBookAir6%2C2+OSX+OSX+10.10.5+build(14F2511)&amp;version=11000006&amp;lang=zh_CN&amp;pass_ticket=hST461UyxA4Jxu8h%2FC41aUyKcv3F0%2BbuArw%2B6MOycxS3NZIJeq%2BwYz27EdqUQNJf\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>1 月 11 日，Onitsuka Tiger 鬼塚虎宣布李宇春成为品牌大中华区代言人</b></a>。今年是品牌创始人鬼塚喜八郎先生诞辰 100 周年，Onitsuka Tiger 鬼塚虎发布 2018 春夏主题“溯·造新生”。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201801121259436Sy7IxCWMhGs1Tk2.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667897\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://www.madisonboom.com/2018/01/12/dove-launches-2017-spring-campaign-with-masichun/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>马思纯出演德芙女孩</b></a>，与演员张颂文演绎一对父女。去年拍摄同一系列贺岁广告的是关晓彤。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=m05319y8lsh&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://www.madisonboom.com/2018/01/11/tiffany-china-new-campaign-follow-your-heart/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>蒂芙尼（Tiffany &amp; Co.）发布&nbsp;Open Heart 18K 玫瑰金项链广告</b></a>，由新晋蒂芙尼中国区首位品牌代言人倪妮演绎。<br></p><p>2018 年 1 月 15 日起，蒂芙尼也将加入微信在 2017 年底发布的“官方精品店”功能，蒂芙尼的入驻为限时性质，将会开设到 1 月底。内售中国地区独家限量版产品，也包括这款致敬传奇设计师艾尔莎·柏瑞蒂的限量版项链。</p><p>目前已开通“精品店”功能的大多是线下品牌连锁店，比如耐克、星巴克、卡地亚、古驰、兰蔻、路易威登、万宝龙、施华洛世奇、蒂芙尼、ZARA 等。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=z0532zauajb&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><h3 finallycleanhtml=\"true\" nocleanhtml=\"true\">值得一提的案例</h3><p><a href=\"http://www.madisonboom.com/2018/01/11/jessie-j-singer-trailer-accused-of-plagiarism/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>《歌手》为 Jessie J 拍的个人宣传片被指出抄袭</b></a>。这支短片和 2017 年 8 月克里斯汀·斯图尔特为香奈儿嘉柏丽尔香水拍摄的广告片在设计上高度相似。但两者相比较下来的效果，简直令人心酸。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=m0532smzb3j&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=a0024yy8m92&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p><b>经历了 2017 的改革风波，戛纳国际创意节这就开始为 2018 年预热了</b>——发布了一支近两年优秀广告的剪辑视频，<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Pmb5NCnyozo\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里查看视频</a>，你能认出里面多少作品？</p><p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 28.0px; font: 18.0px 'Heiti SC Light'; color: #666666; -webkit-text-stroke: #666666} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p><a href=\"http://www.adweek.com/digital/the-most-disturbing-booth-at-ces-is-actually-an-ad-for-netflixs-new-sci-fi-show/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Netflix 为即将上映的电视剧《碳变》在CES上做了个令人毛骨悚然的营销</b></a>，展出了仿真的半裸模特和裹尸袋，这部电视剧讲的是人死后意识可以被移植并复活。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201801121151357qQKETu6hN8smkGS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.561798\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180112115215h5wozeUMnIu4YZAJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.561798\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?time_continue=487&amp;v=p3CjIDcAePM\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Kenzo 发布 9 分钟长春夏广告 “Yo！My Saint” 探索了艺术家与缪斯之间的关系。</b></a>忍过前两分钟就能被惊艳，概念和音乐都很棒。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=e0532fbsw1k&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://tpro.lxustudio.cn/pet\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Tmall Discovery 又出新作</b></a>，为北美进口宠物粮专场投放了一支 H5，讲的是宠物因为吃不好而发脾气，导致全城大乱。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180112115854g7L2UahFGNHIitQr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.628571\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">题图来源:adweek</p>"}